---
description: Enforce DOQS naming conventions and run validators after structural or BOM changes.
globs:
  - "**/okh.toml"
  - "**/bom/*.csv"
  - "**/modules/**"
---

After changing module paths, `okh.toml`, or BOM files, read `doqs/skills/doqs-naming/SKILL.md` and run `python doqs/scripts/validate_all.py` from the machine repository root.
